**Describe the bug**
Getting an error saying - “Found a problem with the content. PowerPoint can attempt to repair it.” while  creating a simple blank pptx

**Desktop (please complete the following information):**
 - Windows
 - Office version [Powerpoint version 2508 Version 19127.20010]
 - .NET Target: (e.g. .NET Framework 9)
 - DocumentFormat.OpenXml Version: (e.g. 2.20.0)


